data.description: If you're looking for the nicest home in the neighborhood, you've found it. Updated from top to bottom with so much to offer. The kitchen, a culinary dream, showcasing updated fixtures, granite counters, and stainless-steel appliances surrounding a generous kitchen island, where memories are made and meals shared. Bathed in natural light from numerous windows, this open-concept home is perfect for those who entertain or growing families looking ofr some extra space.  As you step into the living area, a custom stone gas fireplace stands as a testament to warmth, both in design and atmosphere.  The heart of this home lies in its large master suite, boasting a private bathroom adorned with double sinks and a spacious walk-in closet – a retreat within a retreat. Every inch of this home is adorned with updated high-end fixtures, creating an ambiance of sophistication. The fully finished basement is a sports enthusiast's haven, with a full wet bar, setting the stage for spirited football games and lively gatherings. This is a dream basement and perfect for additional living space.  The exterior beckons with a newly constructed, sprawling patio featuring a fire pit and a bubbling hot tub, embraced by new landscaping that graces the entire yard. Upgraded lighting, both inside and out, elevates the aesthetic, casting a glow on the attention to detail woven into every corner of this residence.  This home is stunning and its one you cant afford to miss.
